	(text "COMPONENT NOTES:\n\nR1, R2, R3, R4, R11, R12: use 1W Resistors.\nFor all other resistors, use 1/4W.\nAll resistors are metal film 1% or better tolerance.\n\nAll screw terminals (J3, J4. J5, J7, J8) are the Phoenix Contact MKDS 1,5 series, 5.08mm pin pitch.\nPin headers (J2, J9, J10) are standard 2.54mm pin pitch male pin headers.\n\nPolarized capacitors (C1, C2, C3, C4, C11, C12) are electrolytics - at least 35V.\n10u capacitors are film.\n100n capacitors are ceramic.\n\nRegulators (U1, U2, U4) are all TO-220 3 pin package.\nHeatsinks used are Same Sky Devices HSE-B20254-035H-01."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 39.37 166.37 0)
